request.description:
Registers a new player with the operating guild and chain.

The user's signature is validated and a GuildMembershipJoinProxy message is sent on their behalf. Once the GuildMembershipJoinProxy message is processed, an ID for the player will be generated and stored in the DB asynchronously.

Since the signup process is asynchronous, login needs to be called separately after the player's ID is generated.
Logs in a player by verfiying a message signed using the player's private key.

response.name: webapp/api/auth/login
